OL,3,CHow Avanti West Coast action during
OL,4,Cfestive period will affect passengers
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We're
OL,7,Fdisappointed our Train Managers who
OL,8,Fare RMT members have voted to decline
OL,9,Fthe very reasonable revised offer made
OL,10,Fto them to resolve the Rest Day
OL,11,FWorking dispute and avoid
OL,12,Finconveniencing our customers. We
OL,13,Fremain open to working with the RMT to
OL,14,Fresolve the dispute."
OL,16,FA Department for Transport
OL,17,Fspokesperson said:
