OL,3,CHow Avanti West Coast action during
OL,4,Cfestive period will affect passengers
OL,6,F"This is incredibly disappointing news
OL,7,Ffor passengers who would have been
OL,8,Fhoping to leave strike action in 2024,
OL,9,Fand we strongly encourage both the RMT
OL,10,Fand Avanti West Coast to get back
OL,11,Faround the table and work in good
OL,12,Ffaith to resolve this as quickly as
OL,13,Fpossible.
OL,15,F"As part of our plans to reform the
OL,16,Frailways, we're determined to move
OL,17,Ftowards a seven-day working week and
OL,18,Fend the overreliance on rest day
OL,19,Fworking, giving passengers the
OL,20,Fcertainty and reliability they
OL,21,Fdeserve."
