OL,3,CHow Avanti West Coast action during
OL,4,Cfestive period will affect passengers
OL,6,FThe National Union of Rail, Maritime
OL,7,Fand Transport Workers (RMT) had
OL,8,Fpreviously agreed to strike on 22,23,
OL,9,Fand 29 December, but suspended strike
OL,10,Faction after receiving a new offer
OL,11,Ffrom Avanti West Coast.
OL,13,FHowever, following a vote on the offer
OL,14,Fon Tuesday 17 December strikes are now
OL,15,Fset to return at the end of the month.
OL,17,FRest Day Working payments and
OL,18,Farrangements over a new technology
OL,19,Fagreement were a couple of the key
OL,20,Ffactors voted on by the RMT.
